    "patch_code": "public void println() throws IOException {\n    if (!newRecord) {\n        super.println();\n    } else {\n        for (String name : headerNames) {\n            Object value = printerConfig.getValueConverter().convert(headerMap.get(name));\n            if (value == null) {\n                value = \"\"; // Add this line to replace null values with \"\"\n            }\n            out.append(format.getStringValue(value))\n              .append(format.getColumnSeparator());\n        }\n        out.setLength(out.length()-1); //remove last separator\n    }\n    out.append(format.getLineEnding());    \n    newRecord = false;\n}",
